Asciinema VS Code Extension
Copyright (c) David Pine

This product is an independent, third-party Visual Studio Code extension for
playing back asciinema recordings. It is not an official asciinema product and
is not affiliated with or endorsed by the asciinema project or its maintainers.

--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Attribution: asciinema
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

This extension plays back files produced by asciinema (https://asciinema.org),
the terminal session recorder created by Marcin Kulik and the asciinema
community. The extension bundles the asciinema-player JavaScript library as a
runtime dependency.

  asciinema-player — https://github.com/asciinema/asciinema-player
  Copyright (c) 2011 Marcin Kulik
  Licensed under the Apache License, Version 2.0
  https://www.apache.org/licenses/LICENSE-2.0

The file-type icon for ``.cast`` files (``media/asciinema-icon.svg``) is the
asciinema play-triangle mark, used here solely to identify the file format and
to describe the origin of the playback engine per Apache-2.0 §6.

The extension's marketplace icon (``media/icon.svg`` / ``media/icon.png``)
incorporates the asciinema play-triangle mark alongside a distinct ``.casts``
label and is used as the mark of this independent extension, not as the
asciinema project's mark.

Please support the upstream project at https://asciinema.org and
https://docs.asciinema.org.
